22222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Symbol;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;">         </span></span>Eviter les conflits de marque lors de la création de votre boutique</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Symbol;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;">         </span></span>Protéger votre propriété intellectuelle</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Symbol;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;">         </span></span>Mettre vos fichiers prospect et clients en conformité avec la CNIL</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Symbol;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;">         </span></span>Gérer vos responsabilités d&#039;éditeur de site (diffamation, e-réputation)</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Symbol;">·</span><span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;">         </span>Mettre en place vos CGV</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Symbol;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;">         </span></span>Quelle fiscalité, quel statut adopter pour votre activité ?</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Inscrivez-vous maintenant avec le code promo PRESTA pour profiter de 100 € de réduction sur la formation !</p>					<div class="gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls right">\n						<a href="javascript:$.fancybox.close();" class="button">Fermer</a>\n						<a href="http://addons.prestashop.com/fr/prestashopformations/19173-serenite-juridique.html" class="button success">En savoir plus</a>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<script>\n	$(document).ready( function () {\n		$(''.gamification_fancybox'').bind(''click'', function () {\n			id_advice = 602;\n			popin_url = ''https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=''+id_advice+''&url='';\n			url = $(''.gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls a.success'').attr(''href'');\n			$(''.gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls a.success'').attr(''href'', popin_url+encodeURIComponent(url));\n			\n			$(''.gamification-tip-infobox'').after(''<img style="display:none" src="https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdvicePopinImg/''+id_advice+''.png" />'');\n			\n		});\n	});\n</script></div>'),
