(48, 1, '2015-11-02 17:24:00', '2015-11-02 16:24:00', 'The SE Santana Standard is a high-quality, articulate guitar for demanding players. With its shorter 24.5” scale length, the SE Santana Standard has a buttery, sweet tone that can go from Santana’s signature lead tone to fat, hard rock rhythm chords. The use of PRS-Designed tremolo and tuners means the tuning reliability is impeccable regardless of playing style. Featuring a striped down all-mahogany body (similar to Paul’s Pre-Factory guitars), a set mahogany neck, rosewood fretboard with bird inlays, and PRS-Designed tremolo and 245 humbuckers, the SE Santana Standard is a tribute to Carlos Santana’s skill and style and offers players a great value and quality.', 'SE Santana Standard', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'se-santana-standard', '', '', '2015-11-02 17:25:54', '2015-11-02 16:25:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?p=48', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2015-11-02 17:24:00', '2015-11-02 16:24:00', 'The SE Santana Standard is a high-quality, articulate guitar for demanding players. With its shorter 24.5” scale length, the SE Santana Standard has a buttery, sweet tone that can go from Santana’s signature lead tone to fat, hard rock rhythm chords. The use of PRS-Designed tremolo and tuners means the tuning reliability is impeccable regardless of playing style. Featuring a striped down all-mahogany body (similar to Paul’s Pre-Factory guitars), a set mahogany neck, rosewood fretboard with bird inlays, and PRS-Designed tremolo and 245 humbuckers, the SE Santana Standard is a tribute to Carlos Santana’s skill and style and offers players a great value and quality.', 'SE Santana Standard', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-02 17:24:00', '2015-11-02 16:24:00', '', 48, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
